parameters: Cat
\SE[2] The Lira family... Is that so? That distinguished family.
King Cordin

\SE\SE[0]Yeah, that place is famous, so you must have heard the
name at least. \SE[0]I want you to infiltrate there.
Cat

\SE[2]That place... is it the moderate faction? \SE[3]While they
may contribute to the development of the country, I don't think
there's any need for them to draw their bows...
King Cordin

\SE[11]That's right. They are excellent. Even from my
perspective. \SE[12]That's why... I suppose.
King Cordin

\SE[15]Someday, they will surely... show the powerless ones a
cruel dream. \SE[0]Holding hands and seeking peace... What a
fleeting dream.
King Cordin

\SE[3]Isn't that just too pitiful? \SE[12]Tragedies always occur
when the have-nots try to become the ones they admire.
King Cordin

\SE[1]The conversation got off track, didn't it? I wonder if
you'll accept the task?
Cat

\SE[32]... Yes, gladly. If it's a royal command, I have no right
to refuse.
King Cordin
\SE[6]Well, that's true. \SE[6]Well then, I'm counting on you.
Cat
\SE[32]...Well then, as you wish.

I was King Cordin's spy. To put it bluntly, I was a spy who
monitored our own country... It has a suspicious ring to it,
doesn't it? Well, it's not that grand of a thing.

I observe influential nobles in 'Cordin' and judge whether they
become a 'threat', then report it... You could say I am a
'supervisor' or 'inspector'.

...Well, anyway. I have been tasked with monitoring the Lira
family. I will be infiltrating as a maid.
